OL,11,FCardinal Matteo Zuppi
OL,13,FMatteo Zuppi was made a cardinal by
OL,14,FPope Francis in 2019.
OL,16,FHe became president of the Episcopal
OL,17,FConference of Italy in 2022, giving
OL,18,Fhim oversight of the country's bishops.
OL,20,FAlongside this, the 69-year-old has
OL,21,Fbeen Archbishop of Bologna since 2015.
