OL,3,CWho are the likely candidates to
OL,4,Csucceed Pope Francis?
OL,6,FIn 2023, Pope Francis appointed Zuppi
OL,7,Fas his special envoy to find a "path
OL,8,Fto peace" for the Ukraine war,
OL,9,Faccording to Vatican News.
OL,11,FThe cardinal went to Kyiv to meet
OL,12,FUkraine's President Volodymyr
OL,13,FZelenskyy, later that year, and also
OL,14,Fmet former US President Joe Biden to
OL,15,Fdeliver a letter from the pope.
OL,17,FAt the end of 2024, Zuppi visited
OL,18,FMoscow for three days to discuss
OL,19,F"humanitarian collaboration", the Holy
OL,20,FSee Press Office said.
