OL,6,FCardinal Peter Turkson
OL,8,FPeter Turkson was made a cardinal by
OL,9,FJohn Paul II in 2003.
OL,11,FThe Ghanaian church leader has held
OL,12,Fnumerous senior positions in the
OL,13,FVatican.
OL,15,FHe has led both the Pontifical Council
OL,16,Ffor Justice and Peace and the
OL,17,FDicastery for the Promotion of
OL,18,FIntegral Human Development.
