OL,3,CWho are the likely candidates to
OL,4,Csucceed Pope Francis?
OL,6,FHe has been hailed as one of Africa's
OL,7,Fmost prominent leaders, and Pope
OL,8,FFrancis sent the cardinal to Africa on
OL,9,Fseveral peacekeeping missions.
OL,11,FMost notably in 2016, he was sent as a
OL,12,Fspecial envoy to pursue peace in South
OL,13,FSudan and handed handwritten letters
OL,14,Ffrom Pope Francis to the leaders of
